 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../088/Intel_8088.xml">
documentary film</link> directed by <link>
Mary Olive Smith</link> and field director <link>
Amy Bucher</link> about the mistreatment of mothers who suffer from childbirth injuries in <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../749/187749.xml">
Ethiopia</link></country>
. In 2007, the film premiered and was chosen by the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../065/12639065.xml">
International Documentary Association</link> as the best feature documentary film of the year. The following year, the film was given theatrical release in the United States.</p>

